ttribute this difference to how the various\nmodels treat the physics of Pauli blocking, correlations, large-angle\nscattering, and diffraction.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Jan 2020 16:37:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-31"}
