ances and thus paving the way for calculating cross\ncovariances between the different probes. This work advances these approximate\nmethods as tools for simulating and analysing surveys data for cosmological\npurposes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Jan 2020 19:00:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 4 Jun 2020 11:06:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-05"}
