 the survey provided us insights on\nimproving StackEmo, with 83% participants having recommended the plugin to\ntheir peers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 31 Jan 2020 04:39:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 17 Jun 2020 13:02:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-18"}
